{
  "id": "5c6277abe7ee9e00173bedc9",
  "title": "独創はひらめかない",
  "created": 1549957037,
  "updated": 1550496726,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5c6277abe7ee9e00173bedc9",
      "text": "独創はひらめかない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1549957037,
      "updated": 1549957084
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6277dcaff09e000051268c",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/943ada0566a6237cdaf33e56d84a5a23]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1549957084,
      "updated": 1549957084
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6277acaff09e0000512687",
      "text": "\t[金出 武雄]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1549957037,
      "updated": 1549957047
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6277efaff09e000051268e",
      "text": "\t[独創]はひらめかない #ひらめき",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1549957103,
      "updated": 1549957115
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6277fbaff09e000051268f",
      "text": "\t\t「[素人発想]、[玄人実行]」の法則",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1549957115,
      "updated": 1549957140
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6277b5aff09e0000512689",
      "text": "\t[Amazon https://amzn.to/2SH2CpY]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1549957045,
      "updated": 1549957099
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6277eaaff09e000051268d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1549957099,
      "updated": 1549957099
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab316aff09e00009ee1ad",
      "text": "目次",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496534,
      "updated": 1550496536
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1af",
      "text": "\t創造へのいざない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496536,
      "updated": 1550496537
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1b0",
      "text": " 第1章　素人のように考え、玄人として実行する－発想、知的体力、シナリオ－",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496537
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1b1",
      "text": "  1遊び心の発想",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496653
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1b2",
      "text": "  2なんと幼稚な、なんと素直な、なんといい加減な考えか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496653
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1b3",
      "text": "  3[成功を疑う]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496653
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1b4",
      "text": "  4[創造は省略から始まる]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496653
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1b5",
      "text": "  5物事を推し進めるためには、[シナリオ]をつくる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496653
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1b6",
      "text": "  6シナリオのキーは、いかに人や社会の役に立つかである",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496653
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1b7",
      "text": "  7[構想力とは、問題を限定する能力である]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496653
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1b8",
      "text": "  8[キス・アプローチ]－単純に、簡単に",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496653
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1b9",
      "text": "  9知的体力－[集中力]とは、自分が問題そのものになること",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496653
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1ba",
      "text": "  10[できるやつほど迷う]ものだ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496653
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1bb",
      "text": "  11[「できない」から次が始まる]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496653
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1bc",
      "text": "  12[アイデアは「人に話して」発展する]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496653
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1bd",
      "text": "  13私の原体験をこじつける",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496653
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1be",
      "text": "  14「玄人発想、素人実行」－これはまずい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496653
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1bf",
      "text": "  15独創、創造に関する三つの反常識的説",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496653
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab35baff09e00009ee1e7",
      "text": "  \t[独創はひらめかない]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496604,
      "updated": 1550496653
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1c0",
      "text": " 第2章コンピュータが人にチャレンジしている－問題解決能力、教育－",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496537
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1c1",
      "text": "  16コンピュータが人にチャレンジしている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496647
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1c2",
      "text": "  17[人もコンピュータも計算する機械]である",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496647
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1c3",
      "text": "  18人とコンピュータは違うか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496647
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1c4",
      "text": "  19コンピュータは人より知能的になる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496647
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1c5",
      "text": "  20思考力、判断力は問題解決に挑戦することで伸びる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496647
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1c6",
      "text": "  21例題を考え、解くことが理解を深める最もよい方法である",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496647
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1c7",
      "text": "  22考える力を育てる教科書の記述法",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496647
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1c8",
      "text": "  23創造力、企画力の土台となる記憶力",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496647
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1c9",
      "text": "  24思考力、記憶力は、繰り返しやることで伸びる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496647
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1ca",
      "text": "  25異なるジャンルの人と知的に対決",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496647
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1cb",
      "text": "  26「[ゆとり教育]」と「[詰め込み教育]」を弁証法的に考察する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496667
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1cc",
      "text": " 第3章自分の考えを表現し、説得する－国際化時代の講演・会話・書き方の技術－",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496537
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1cd",
      "text": "  27説得する－黙っていてはわからない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496677
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1ce",
      "text": "  28前置きなしに話す－こう言えば、ああ思う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496677
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1cf",
      "text": "  29結果は説明ほどにものを言い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496677
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1d0",
      "text": "  30[説明して納得させるのではなく、納得させてから説明する]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496695
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1d1",
      "text": "  31相手の目を見て話す",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496677
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1d2",
      "text": "  32ほめて伸ばす、争点を明らかにして話す",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496677
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1d3",
      "text": "  33たとえと例は違う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496677
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1d4",
      "text": "  34英語は「外国人にしてはうまいな」と思われるぐらいがよい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496677
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1d5",
      "text": "  35英会話上達の秘訣",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496677
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1d6",
      "text": "  36論文や人を説得する書き物は推理小説と同じである",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496677
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1d7",
      "text": "  37「起承転結」のコンビネーション",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496677
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1d8",
      "text": "  38「結」を演出する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496677
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1d9",
      "text": "  39提案書は相手が上司に説明しやすく書く",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496677
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1da",
      "text": "  40発表と英語に関する三つのアドバイス",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496677
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1db",
      "text": " 第4章　[決断と明示のスピード]が求められている－日本と世界、自分と他人を考える－",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496717
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1dc",
      "text": "  41日本に求められるのは「[知のスピード]」である",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496712
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1dd",
      "text": "  42インターネットが社会を再構築する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496707
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1de",
      "text": "  43「自分がどう見られるか」の強迫観念と存在感",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496707
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1df",
      "text": "  44「日本独自」をかくれみのにしない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496707
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1e0",
      "text": "  45人を引っ張るリーダーシップ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496707
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1e1",
      "text": "  46うまくいかない時もあるあっさりと方向転換しよう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496707
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1e2",
      "text": "  47評価とは本来主観的なものである",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496707
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1e3",
      "text": "  48「自分が決める」という勇気",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496707
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1e4",
      "text": " おわりに　楽しく問題解決を",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496537
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ab318aff09e00009ee1e5",
      "text": " 新版あとがき　十年後の日本へのメッセージ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550496537,
      "updated": 1550496537
    }
  ]
}